BISMARCK , N.D. ( AP ) - Officials are trying to boost the number of dairy farms in North Dakota .
Members of the North Dakota Dairy Coalition recently met with representatives of crop commodity groups .
State Agriculture Commissioner Doug Goehring says rebuilding the state 's dairy industry will give crop and forage producers more local markets .
